---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="Learn about our privacy practices and how we protect your information.">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary">
      Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you visit our website.
    </p>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary">
        We may collect the following types of information:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2 text-text-secondary">
        <li>Personal information you provide, such as name and email address.</li>
        <li>Information automatically collected when you visit our site, like IP address, browser type, and pages visited.</li>
        <li>Cookies and similar tracking technologies to improve user experience.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary">We use your information to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2 text-text-secondary">
        <li>Provide and improve our services and website functionality.</li>
        <li>Send newsletters or updates if you subscribe.</li>
        <li>Analyze website usage to improve content and user experience.</li>
        <li>Protect our website from fraud and unauthorized activities.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">3. Sharing Your Information</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary">
        We do not sell or rent your personal information. We may share information with trusted third parties for:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2 text-text-secondary">
        <li>Service providers who help us operate the website and send communications.</li>
        <li>Legal reasons or to protect our rights and property.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">4. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary">
        Our website uses cookies and similar technologies to enhance your experience, analyze site traffic, and deliver personalized content. You can manage cookies through your browser settings.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">5. Data Security</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary">
        We implement reasonable security measures to protect your personal information. However, no website or transmission over the Internet can be guaranteed to be 100% secure.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">6. Third-Party Links</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary">
        Our website may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these websites. Please review their privacy policies before providing any personal information.
      </p>
    </section>

<section class="mt-8">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Account Deletion & Data Removal</h2>
  <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary">
    If you choose to delete your account from our website, all personal information associated with your account will be automatically and permanently removed from our database. This includes any data you have provided, your activity history, and any other identifiable information. 
  </p>
  <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary">
    Please note that some data may remain in backup copies for a short period due to our system processes, but it will not be used for any purposes and will be permanently deleted in line with our data retention policy.
  </p>
</section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">8. Updates to This Policy</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary">
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Updates will be posted on this page, and the "last updated" date will be revised accordingly.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">9. Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary">
        If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, feel free to contact us at: 
        <br />
        <a href="/contact" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Contact form</a>
      </p>
    </section>

    <p class="mt-12 text-sm text-gray-500">Last updated: September 1, 2025</p>
  </main>
</Layout>
